{"tid":2403890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劉淑儀： 與女兒分隔兩地的大除夕","createTime":"2021-02-11T11:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T14:54:44.000Z","uid":230530,"like":18,"dislike":245,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"f6eaaa5a0e2b89103ee630c9819592abbd2b371a","tid":2403890,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"【與女兒分隔兩地的大除夕】<br />\n<br />\n女兒在英國工作，由於來往港英航班暫停，兩地交通斷絕往來，她與不少滯留當地的港人一樣，與家人被逼分隔兩地，我倆也是獨個兒在家過節，度過一個最寂寞的大除夕。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，但我亦自得其樂，早已安排一頓豐富晚飯，取其家肥屋潤好意頭。我會與如家人一樣，服務多年的菲傭「撐檯腳」。我將首次在家欣賞春晚直播節目，我曾瀏覽節目流程，發現劉德華、周杰倫、陳偉霆等知名藝人均參與表演，可說是中港台巨星雲集，相信其演出將會十分精彩，令人期待。<br />\n<br />\n近日香港疫情漸趨緩和，希望新一年牛到疫除，香港早日戰勝疫情，病痛遠離，經濟復甦，讓香港得以走出陰霾，重拾東方之珠光茫。同時亦祝願各位市民身體健康，心想事成。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deytVhJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdeytVhJ.png&h=b27a443b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdf0911296746225f7c1582ad76b4c60e378a026","tid":2403890,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef6eaa41475e892e2f3728c96a3278c7b437bc6","tid":2403890,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"4ba5586325ac170f8f64b47668c62574d1c7b6bb","tid":2403890,"uid":231480,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"心繫英國"},{"pid":"c2d2af6c0d48a7c6dc2fd5040d9f24375b336a00","tid":2403890,"uid":108016,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"二等公民？"},{"pid":"7653185524de8aac0bd178bbd6330d0755c63229",